OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780369438
OL,3,CQuentin Blake Centre for Illustration
OL,4,Cto showcase 'overlooked' art form
OL,6,FSir Quentin Blake's two-decade long
OL,7,Fdream to create the UK's first
OL,8,Fpermanent space for illustration is
OL,9,Ffinally a reality.
OL,11,FIn 2002 the illustrator, 93, best
OL,12,Fknown for collaborating with Roald
OL,13,FDahl, founded the House of
OL,14,FIllustration, which has now moved into
OL,15,Fa former waterworks in Clerkenwell,
OL,16,Fcentral London.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
