FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780369438
OL,3,CQuentin Blake Centre for Illustration
OL,4,Cto showcase 'overlooked' art form
OL,6,FOpening on Friday, the Quentin Blake
OL,7,FCentre for Illustration includes three
OL,8,Fexhibition spaces, a cafe, shop,
OL,9,Fgardens and free spaces including a
OL,10,Flibrary with more than 1,800 books,
OL,11,Fand creative studio.
OL,13,FOne of the exhibition spaces will be
OL,14,Fdedicated to his work, the first
OL,15,Fselection titled Performance. It will
OL,16,Fshowcase theatrical influences and
OL,17,Ffeature more than 100 original and
OL,18,Frarely seen drawings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780369438
OL,3,CQuentin Blake Centre for Illustration
OL,4,Cto showcase 'overlooked' art form
OL,6,FHighlights include a caricature of
OL,7,FLaurence Olivier in The Entertainer,
OL,8,Fdrawn to accompany a theatre review in
OL,9,F1957, and pieces he created for a
OL,10,FFolio Society edition of Beckett's
OL,11,FWaiting for Godot.
OL,13,FThe exhibition also features
OL,14,Fillustrations and preliminary drawings
OL,15,Ffor The Enormous Crocodile, which was
OL,16,Fpublished in 1978 ` the first Dahl
OL,17,Fbook he illustrated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
