FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780369438
OL,3,CQuentin Blake Centre for Illustration
OL,4,Cto showcase 'overlooked' art form
OL,6,FAsked about what has seen him become
OL,7,Fsuch a beloved figure over decades,
OL,8,Fshe said: "He's just great at telling
OL,9,Fa story and has a very fluid,
OL,10,Fgestural, kind of drawing line. The
OL,11,Flines aren't joined up, and the
OL,12,Fcolours fly out of the line too, which
OL,13,Fgives his work great movement and
OL,14,Fmakes you excited to turn the pages of
OL,15,Fhis books."
OL,17,FThe opening of the centre will also
OL,18,Finclude illustrator Murugiah's first
OL,19,Fsolo show.
OL,26,@pD@KOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780369438
OL,3,CQuentin Blake Centre for Illustration
OL,4,Cto showcase 'overlooked' art form
OL,6,FTitled Ever Feel Like, the artist's
OL,7,Fworks draw upon his Sri Lankan
OL,8,Fheritage and Welsh upbringing, in
OL,9,Fwhich he reflects on his identity and
OL,10,Fmakes references to Hollywood film and
OL,11,FSri Lankan motifs.
OL,13,FThe other exhibition, Queer as Comics,
OL,14,Fmarks the first major exhibition on
OL,15,Fqueer comic-making in the UK, spanning
OL,16,Fthe 1940s to the present day.
OL,18,FGlen said she wanted everyone to leave
OL,19,Fthe centre "looking differently at the
OL,20,Fworld around them".
OL,26,@{D@LOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780369438
OL,3,CQuentin Blake Centre for Illustration
OL,4,Cto showcase 'overlooked' art form
OL,6,F"We want them to notice the
OL,7,Fillustrations that are part of our
OL,8,Feveryday lives, and to think about the
OL,9,Fcommunication that's within those,
OL,10,Fthose pictures, to think about the way
OL,11,Fthat illustration persuades us and
OL,12,Ftells us stories.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780369438
OL,3,CQuentin Blake Centre for Illustration
OL,4,Cto showcase 'overlooked' art form
OL,6,F"We also want everyone to leave
OL,7,Fknowing that they too can be an
OL,8,Fillustrator that with a few simple
OL,9,Ftools, whether that is some torn up
OL,10,Fpieces of paper used as a collage,
OL,11,Fwhether that is pencil and pen,
OL,12,Fwhether that's through digital media,
OL,13,Fthat they too can tell their own story
OL,14,Fas an illustrator."
OL,16,FLast week Sir Quentin, who continues
OL,17,Fto draw every day, visited the centre.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780369438
OL,3,CQuentin Blake Centre for Illustration
OL,4,Cto showcase 'overlooked' art form
OL,6,FGlen said: "He has been the most
OL,7,Fincredible, tireless, and generous
OL,8,Fchampion of illustration, and utterly
OL,9,Fcommitted to making this project
OL,10,Fhappen, and he is thrilled."
OL,26,@nD@LOUrD@\O]
